PrecisAppointment of MARK T. MOSSEY of the city of Iqaluit in Nunavut, Barrister-at-law, to be a Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut, a Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Northwest Territories, and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Yukon, during his tenure of office as a Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice.
